---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Mobile Applications | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional mobile app development services in the UAE. Cross-platform apps for Android and iPhone using Flutter, with AI and IoT integration."
  path="/services/mobile-apps/"
  image="/img/og-mobile-apps.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="software-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Mobile Applications</h2>
      <p>
        Mobile is the primary channel through which businesses engage with
        their customers in the UAE — one of the highest smartphone penetration
        markets in the world. At GeneralSoft, we build mobile applications that
        are performant, intuitive, and connected to your backend systems. We
        specialize in cross-platform development with Flutter, delivering
        native-quality apps for both Android and iPhone from a single codebase.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mobile development goes beyond simple UI work. We integrate mobile
        apps with cloud services, IoT devices, AI models, and enterprise
        systems — creating connected experiences that drive real business
        value.
      </p>

      <h3>Mobile Development Capabilities</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Cross-Platform Apps</h4>
          <p>
            Flutter-based applications that deliver native performance on both
            Android and iOS from a single codebase.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>AI-Powered Mobile</h4>
          <p>
            Mobile apps with integrated AI capabilities including real-time
            object recognition, NLP, and predictive analytics.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>IoT-Connected Apps</h4>
          <p>
            Mobile applications that connect to IoT devices, sensors, and smart
            infrastructure via MQTT and cloud platforms.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Enterprise Mobile</h4>
          <p>
            Secure enterprise mobile applications integrated with CRM, ERP, and
            backend business systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven Mobile Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our mobile portfolio includes consumer apps, enterprise mobility
          solutions, and IoT-connected applications deployed in production.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Recycling App with AI Object Recognition</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Apr 2023 – Aug 2023</span>
            <span class="role">Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed a cross-platform mobile application (Android and iPhone)
            that uses AI-powered real-time object recognition to identify and
            classify recyclable materials. Users point their camera at an item
            and the app instantly identifies the material type, provides
            recycling instructions, and locates nearby recycling centers. Built
            with Flutter, Firebase, and integrated IoT sensors for smart bin
            connectivity.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Flutter</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Firebase</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">AI</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Real-Time Object Recognition</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">IoT</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Android</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">iOS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>App For Hygiene Service Providers</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Sep 2021 – Dec 2022</span>
            <span class="role">Media Consultant & Trainer. Web & App Developer.</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed a cross-platform mobile application for hygiene service
            providers in Abu Dhabi. Built with Flutter and a microservices
            backend architecture. The app manages service scheduling, customer
            management, real-time service tracking, and payment processing.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Flutter</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Microservices</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Firebase</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Android</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">iOS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Mobile Application for Acute Healthcare — Germany</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jul 2005 – Aug 2005</span>
            <span class="role">Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed a mobile application for acute healthcare in Germany using
            C++, BizTalk Messaging, and BizTalk Orchestration. The application
            processed inbound data including flat files and EDI documents with
            attachments. Wrote a custom BizTalk DICOM adapter for medical
            imaging integration. Used GIS location information for activating
            and routing healthcare response algorithms.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">C++</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">DICOM</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">EDI</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">GIS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Healthcare</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Corporate Store Apps — Windows Phone & RT</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Oct 2014 – Jan 2015</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Built corporate store applications for Windows Phone and Windows RT
            as part of an enterprise ERP migration project. The apps provided
            mobile access to inventory, order management, and business
            analytics. Integrated with Azure AD for secure authentication and
            on-premises backend systems.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Windows Phone</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Windows RT</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SAP</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cross-Platform:</strong> Flutter, FlutterFlow</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Firebase, .NET, NodeJS, Python</li>
        <li><strong>AI Integration:</strong> TensorFlow Lite, ML Kit, Custom Vision</li>
        <li><strong>IoT:</strong> MQTT, Azure IoT Hub, BLE</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud:</strong> Firebase, Azure, AWS</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Common questions about our mobile app development services.
        </p>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>Why Flutter for cross-platform development?</summary>
            <p>
              Flutter delivers near-native performance on both Android and iOS
              from a single codebase, significantly reducing development time
              and maintenance costs. It provides a rich set of pre-built widgets
              that follow platform-specific design patterns, so your app looks
              and feels native on both platforms.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>Can you integrate AI features into mobile apps?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We have experience integrating AI capabilities into mobile
              apps including real-time object recognition, natural language
              processing, and predictive analytics. We use TensorFlow Lite and
              ML Kit for on-device processing, and cloud AI services for more
              complex workloads.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>Do you publish apps to the App Store and Google Play?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We handle the entire app store submission process including
              preparing app store listings, screenshots, privacy policies, and
              compliance documentation. We also manage ongoing updates and
              version submissions.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Let's Build Something Great Together</h2>
        <p>
          Ready to build a mobile app for your business? Get in touch with our
          team today.
        </p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a
              href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/contact/"
              ><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong
              ><br />Get in touch</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong
            ><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
